    {
        "content": "<p>The syntax I gave had a very brief reign.  I think the new syntax should be</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">have</span> <span class=\"n\">h1</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">linear_combination</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">h.1</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">h.2</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
